title: gBsSndRpt error when trying to open up league of legends launcher
body:
I've been having issues opening league of legends launcher, i have tried reinstalling the game twice, running as admin but this error keeps popping up when i try to open LOL.
Help!

gBsSndRpt

Expexcted argument 'i'

replies.body:
Hey there,

I'm sorry for the delayed response, are you still experiencing this issue?

Have you tried [updating your GPU drivers](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201761974-Bug-Splat-and-Game-Crashes#wq2)?
